company_name: AGRAR-PRODUKTIONS- UND VERARBEITUNGS GMBH NEUENDORF B/IVEN
information: The company AGRAR-PRODUKTIONS- UND VERARBEITUNGS GMBH NEUENDORF B/IVEN, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1991, which operates in the Cereals and grains industry. It also operates in the Fruit industries. It is based in Iven, Germany.
